name: Dano Nelson
coverLetter: I use to do alot of trimming back in the 80s&90s ! I'm  great with my hands ! I'm  honest , trustworthy & dependable ! I'd love full time work for as long as possible ! I'm a welder by trade & just got done fighting fires in Ca. & Oregon ! I'd appreciate a chance to prove my work ethic ! I have no problem living on site while working!
